                                        several words (e.g. <locus target="#12r #13v"/>).</desc>
                                </item>

                                <item xml:id="e2">
                                    <desc>Writing exercises and crude drawings on <locus from="1r"
                                            to="1v"/> and <locus from="15v" to="16v"/>; scribbles
                                        and doodles in the margins throughout the manusicript;
                                        erased notes in bown ink in the lower margin of <locus
                                            from="9r" to="11r"/>.</desc>
                                </item>

                                <item xml:id="e3">
