                                        the inner side of the front board. Below, another sticker
                                        with the signature ‘Ms 1’ printed on it is glued. A note is
                                        written in pencil in the inners side of the front and back
                                        bord respectively with the shelf mark 'Ethiopian Ms 1' and
                                        the remark 'Hymn to Yared'.</desc>
                                    <!--<desc>to be checked: for correctnes and for completion of the note</desc>-->
